FLY UTA TO AUSTRALIA
and get TAHITI free
Australia is sky-climbing cities and warm golden
beaches. Oyster-stuffed steaks and kangaroo tail
soup. Vigorous, high-spirited people. Tahiti is a
calm paradise of blue lagoons, soaring purple
mountains, scarlet hibiscus, and graceful, golden-
skinned Polynesians. You can enjoy both of these
worlds when you fly UTA French Airlines.
A "Tahiti Break" is yours at no extra fare on your
way to Australia. In fact, while you're visiting Tahiti,
you can take a round-trip flying boat excursion to
fabled Bora Bora at no extra fare as well. Then,
from Tahiti, UTA's DC-8 Fan Jets whisk you to
fabulous ful and on to Sydney, gateway to the
booming land of Australia.
UTA's new, lower excursion fares let you fly to
Sydney for as low as $/56, round trip from the
West Coast. Like to know more? See your travel
agent or any office of AIR FRANCE, our general
agent. Or send the coupon.
UTA FRENCH AIRLINES
P. O. Box 4157, North Hollywood, California 91607
